{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2190704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用搓澡巾的cz表示，虽然知道很多人只打沐浴液，自己夏天偶尔也这么干，但还是对这个比例大受震撼。。。现在也时常尝试只打沐浴液，发现根本洗不干净灰啊……冲掉沫之后部分地区手一搓还掉灰轱辘，是cz哪儿操作错了嘛", "timestamp": 1627886864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190707, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190704, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 用沐浴球啊", "timestamp": 1627886891, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190704, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我大受震撼 我为什么不知道有灰", "timestamp": 1627886921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190704, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就继续搓直到搓不出来为止哈哈，我一般先不打沐浴液，淋着水只搓，搓差不多了打沐浴液再搓，之后就基本搓不下来灰了", "timestamp": 1627887090, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "南方人甚至没见过搓澡巾，大受震撼了（沐浴球倒是见过但极少用）", "timestamp": 1627887136, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190748, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190707, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 用了 效果似乎没有搓澡巾凌厉 之后再改进一下各部位加工要求试试。。。", "timestamp": 1627887408, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190756, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190721, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 同Dave", "timestamp": 1627887494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般几周到一个月搓一次，搓澡太浪费时间精力了", "timestamp": 1627887587, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190768, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "平时就只是沐浴露或者单纯用水冲", "timestamp": 1627887605, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190778, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190709, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 举个例子 侧腰、小臂外侧、上背部cz都经常冲完沐浴露还有灰。仔细想想，可能因为以前一直搓灰所以打沐浴露的时候不会用多少力气，就是抹匀出沫就完事了。或许只用沐浴露的话也需要大力揉搓？", "timestamp": 1627887698, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190707, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 用的，这东西除了辅助起泡之外还能当打磨板用的嘛……", "timestamp": 1627887765, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190717, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 徒手嘛，那真不如搓澡巾爽快了哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1627887853, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190803, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190778, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那我下次试试看！", "timestamp": 1627887935, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190803, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能前几次用会比较疼，多适应就会get到爽点了，跟热水泡脚有点像。可以先在皮肤较厚的地方试，比如手臂和腿部外侧、胸腹、侧腰、手背等。希望dz也能获得搓澡的快乐hhhhh", "timestamp": 1627888551, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190897, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190803, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 别过分用力，过火也是会搓破皮的", "timestamp": 1627888605, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190914, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190897, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 呜呜呜呜不敢用搓澡巾 我先试试沐浴球吧", "timestamp": 1627888801, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2190995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190914, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 🤣没必要这么紧张 只要不是疼了还使劲搓就没事 反正戴在自己手上 可以直接上搓澡巾试试", "timestamp": 1627889448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191012, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424415, "reply_to": 2190995, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 猴！", "timestamp": 1627889568, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 424415, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "#423868\n昨天和朋友讨论起这个话题\n我是前者 他是后者 彼此没听说过另一种洗澡方式\n于是我就发了这条树洞并将统计结果发给他 他表示大受震撼hhh", "timestamp": 1627886490, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627889569, "url": "", "vote": {}}}